## GigGuard Project Rules
- Stack: React PWA + Node.js/Express + Python FastAPI + Supabase + n8n
- Always use conventional commits: feat:, fix:, docs:
- Never commit .env files
- Never install paid npm packages — free tiers only
- Keep ML models inside /ml/models/
- Ask permission before running any database migration
- All API secrets must come from .env, never hardcoded